            <span class="text-[#0d7377]">PR</span><span class="text-white">O</span><span class="text-[#0d7377]">UDTEK</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Professional RFID cards, smart cards, and RFID tags manufacturer since 2008. Located in Shenzhen, China.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/proudtek" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-9 h-9 bg-gray-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#0d7377] transition-colors" aria-label="LinkedIn">
